reviewText:
Another fantastic piece of work by Anita !!!  This is a another funny, hit the nail on the head video by Ms Renfro.  I recommend this and all of Anita's videos.  In fact,  I recently had my womans group over for a "Movie Night" of Anita and we all laughed till we cried !!

I urge you to own this tape AND to give one as a gift to spread some laughter in another persons life !

Thanks again !!!
Ordered this and when I played it worked great. Had no problems with playing this and came in the condition just like the description said.
Outright funny look at women as women, spouses and copers with this world's funny foibles.  Great to share viewing with your partner.
Love this video and this lady.
